{"tid":1924044,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"依家去外地讀master係咪倒錢落海？","createTime":"2020-03-13T12:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T06:12:25.000Z","uid":157336,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e368acddd908858848465e7a7c481e9ffe09de48","tid":1924044,"uid":157336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:15:21.000Z","msg":"我細妹上年三大畢業，bachelor成績唔算好，依家話要走去澳洲讀master，用兩年時間等香港穩定少少，順便轉行<br />\n<br />\n但我同屋企人覺得肺炎好撚危險，澳洲仲要咁多支那人，衰啲講句半年後疫情點都未知，依家仲要俾哂學費、宿舍費個啲，正間冇得去真係倒錢落海！<br />\n<br />\n而且佢本身都有份工，現在大把人工都搵唔到，佢依個時候辭職讀書好似好戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n我勸咗佢㗎喇，但佢又計劃好哂"},{"pid":"7816ce3f29618421ccf096bbdcf453b86b6e06de","tid":1924044,"uid":147916,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:17:41.000Z","msg":"係，去澳洲都係戇鳩"},{"pid":"42d99d0fc509c99debb4c8efaf51a6cc41f5165c","tid":1924044,"uid":127410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:18:26.000Z","msg":"會買唔到口罩"},{"pid":"845a6f0df619b5ac7ebe41a70874c28bb565af98","tid":1924044,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:21:09.000Z","msg":"佢人生佢作主啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過錢係佢出先好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e1bfac3bcde71cdf29d2ef23826fbb68c7b6c7","tid":1924044,"uid":7268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:33:35.000Z","msg":"可能下一份工更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ba0f63dd6d0bb6587fb311ebbdb24bbbc4a4a7","tid":1924044,"uid":153722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:33:45.000Z","msg":"早兩年聽講係bne讀master兼留低做兩年相關野就可以移民<br />\n如果仲work既係好野黎"},{"pid":"b0c73d6d120ccbda732faf0ecc7d94a669782208","tid":1924044,"uid":13250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:38:06.000Z","msg":"去到澳洲會唔會都係宿舍用zoom上堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實同係香港讀冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dace2ae6f3ae30f5eac244b20fd6ea6cf2d7b596","tid":1924044,"uid":153722,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:38:47.000Z","msg":"比例上香港咪仲多支那人<br />\n<br />\n佢自己又afford到唔係洗你屋企錢<br />\n依家澳元又低位<br />\n我覺你妹無問題囉<br />\n<br />\n難道佢要完左個degree就要攬住份工到死？<br />\n佢無得揀自己條路黎行？<br />\n兩年蝕唔起咩依家<br />\n<br />\n你個妹條路未行<br />\n我唔知之後會行到點<br />\n唔知有冇得識個鬼仔 當地識個abc結婚定居<br />\n<br />\n但目光比你同你老母遠大就一定係"},{"pid":"5f16009c1601e996fd6ab09a4938d326ff322c23","tid":1924044,"uid":157336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0c73d6d120ccbda732faf0ecc7d94a669782208","tid":1924044,"uid":13250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:38:06.000Z","msg":"去到澳洲會唔會都係宿舍用zoom上堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實同係香港讀冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:48:41.000Z","msg":"就係半年後點都未知... 到時澳洲仲要冬天，可能大爆發"},{"pid":"ea25a6c79b8238f804ca44f4823b2d4a379896cf","tid":1924044,"uid":157336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f9ba0f63dd6d0bb6587fb311ebbdb24bbbc4a4a7","tid":1924044,"uid":153722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:33:45.000Z","msg":"早兩年聽講係bne讀master兼留低做兩年相關野就可以移民<br />\n如果仲work既係好野黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:51:14.000Z","msg":"移民嚟講澳洲係易啲，但就係感覺澳洲遲早都俾支那完全侵佔，咁嘅話移過去都未必係好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ed66e46712d84e4b564c76974fd69031df69d9","tid":1924044,"uid":77547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:52:45.000Z","msg":"而家全世界俾支共攬炒，都唔知點俾意見好。。。"},{"pid":"cbe36efd84f8c68d62058337aa27c408b5af8e22","tid":1924044,"uid":157336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"845a6f0df619b5ac7ebe41a70874c28bb565af98","tid":1924044,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:21:09.000Z","msg":"佢人生佢作主啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.